Second Department,

May, 1937.

(May 4, 1937.) In the Matter of the Application of Edwin D. Ford, Jr., for Admission to Practice as an Attorney and Counselor at Law. (From the State of Minnesota.)

Motion by petitioner for leave to resubmit his application granted. Application granted. Present — Hagarty, Davis, Johnston, Adel and Close, JJ.
